  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>By combining your saliva with your clan's unique chakra, you imbue it with fire-like properties for an unexpected assault. You fire two bolts of your chakra imbued saliva at a target or one for two targets. Make two ranged ninjutsu attacks against the target. On a hit, the target takes fire damage equal to 1d6+2 for each bolt. Each time you deal damage to a creature with this jutsu, it must make a Constitution saving throw, gaining the burned condition on a failed save. A flammable object hit by this jutsu ignites if it isn't being worn or carried.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks</strong>:For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3, and increase the damage per bolt by 1d6+2</p>",
